"ngram\": \"we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"the first medals\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We knew coming into the Olympics that Amit Elor was one of Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s best chances at a gold medal in wrestling, and her weight class was up on the first day.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"Amit Elor\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"best chances\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestling\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"her weight class\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"the first day\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She won her first three matches in dominating fashion and will be in the finals of the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 68-kg freestyle competition, which starts at 12:15 p.m.\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her first three matches\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"fashion\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 68-kg freestyle competition\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ET.\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ET\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But her gold medal match will be the 15th bout on that mat, so it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s tough to give an exact start time.\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her gold medal match\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"the 15th bout\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2203}, {\"ngram\": \"that mat\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"an exact start time\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I haven\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t brought up handball very much in this space, but it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s always a fan favorite.\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"handball\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"this space\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are now out of group play and into the knockout rounds.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"group play\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"the knockout rounds\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All four women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s quarterfinals will be on Tuesday, then the four men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s games will be on Friday.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All four women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s quarterfinals\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"the four men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s games\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Games are a full hour and they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll be running throughout the day.\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Games\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"a full hour\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So now is a perfect time to pick a team and hop on a bandwagon.\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a perfect time\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"a bandwagon\